---
// Solution section — "Ce que nous faisons" — 2 columns
---
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-sand" aria-label="Ce que nous faisons">
  <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
    <h2 class="text-center text-[2rem] md:text-[3rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.15] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-12 md:mb-16 fade-in">
      Ce que nous faisons
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <!-- Visibilité IA -->
      <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 md:p-10 bg-cream transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-terracotta fade-in">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 6V2H8" />
            <path d="M15 11v2" />
            <path d="M2 12h2" />
            <path d="M20 12h2" />
            <path d="M20 16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H8.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 4 20.286V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
            <path d="M9 11v2" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-[1.75rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal">
            Visibilité IA
          </h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Apparaître dans les recommandations ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity et Claude
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Optimiser votre empreinte numérique pour les moteurs de réponse IA
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Données structurées et signaux de confiance pour les algorithmes d'IA
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Visibilité Google -->
      <div class="border border-warmgray p-8 md:p-10 bg-cream transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-terracotta fade-in">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-terracotta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34" />
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-[1.75rem] font-serif font-normal leading-[1.2] text-charcoal">
            Visibilité Google
          </h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Classement Google Maps et Map Pack dans votre arrondissement
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Optimisation complète de votre fiche Google Business Profile
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-base md:text-lg font-sans font-normal leading-relaxed text-stone">
            <span class="mt-2 block w-1.5 h-1.5 shrink-0 bg-terracotta" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Stratégie d'avis, contenu local et maillage d'annuaires
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
